      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m parting ways with this absolute gem, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014the paint is sparkling, the interior is flawless, and it drives like an absolute dream. It\u2019s been garage-kept and pampered since the day I got it. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and ready for its next adventure, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
