    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a concours-level specimen featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis is structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry utilizing Bilstein B16 dampers. Every mechanical component, from the high-pressure VANOS system to the variable M differential lock, operates with factory-spec precision. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the aesthetic condition is impeccable, showing zero signs of track use or environmental wear. This is a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
