      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that represents the pinnacle of its model year. This car is in showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, and has been protected with a multi-layer ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no visible wear to the bolsters, and the original carpets are protected by factory mats. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, operates with precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified specialists. This vehicle comes with a comprehensive binder of service records, two sets of keys, and the original window sticker. It drives with the tightness and responsiveness of a brand-new car, offering an uncompromising experience for the most detail-oriented enthusiast.",
